docs.title: _parse_nums(inputs)
docs.text:
Parse nums

Parameters:

  • inputs (list[str]) –

    List of strings

Source code in .tox/doc-deploy/lib/python3.12/site-packages/imppkg/harmony.py 
def _parse_nums(inputs: list[str]) -> list[float]:
    """Parse nums

    Parameters:
        inputs: List of strings
    """
    try:
        return [float(num) for num in inputs]
    except ValueError:
        return []

def _calculate_result(nums: list[float]) -> float:
    """Print print print"""
    try:
        return harmonic_mean(nums)
    except ZeroDivisionError:
        return 0.0
